OL,3,CTrump says Iran's response to
OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FIran said it wants negotiations to
OL,8,Ffocus on permanently ending its war
OL,9,Fwith the US in its latest response to
OL,10,Fceasefire proposals, conveyed by
OL,11,FPakistani mediators.
OL,13,FBut US President Donald Trump quickly
OL,14,Frejected the Islamic Republic's
OL,15,Fresponse as "TOTALLY UNACCEPTABLE!"
OL,16,Fwithout elaborating further.
OL,26,@wD@MOUwD@cO]
