OL,3,CTrump says Iran's response to
OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FIran seeks to end the war on all
OL,8,Ffronts, including in Lebanon, where
OL,9,FIsrael is fighting the Iranian-backed
OL,10,FHezbollah militant group, and to
OL,11,Fensure the security of shipping, state
OL,12,FTV said.
OL,14,FWashington's latest proposal addressed
OL,15,Fa deal to end the war, reopen the
OL,16,FStrait of Hormuz and roll back Iran's
OL,17,Fnuclear program.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
