OL,3,CTrump says Iran's response to
OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FTrump earlier on social media accused
OL,8,FTehran of "playing games" with the
OL,9,FUnited States for nearly 50 years,
OL,10,Fadding: "They will be laughing no
OL,11,Flonger!"
OL,13,FTrump is giving diplomacy "every
OL,14,Fchance we possibly can before going
OL,15,Fback to hostilities," US ambassador to
OL,16,Fthe United Nations Mike Waltz told ABC
OL,17,Fearlier.
