OL,3,CTrump says Iran's response to
OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FIran's new supreme leader, Mojtaba
OL,8,FKhamenei, who has not been seen or
OL,9,Fheard publicly since the war began,
OL,10,F"issued new and decisive directives
OL,11,Ffor the continuation of operations and
OL,12,Fthe powerful confrontation with the
OL,13,Fenemies" while meeting with the head
OL,14,Fof the joint military command, the
OL,15,Fstate broadcaster reported.
OL,17,FDrone attacks target Gulf Arab nations
