OL,3,CTrump says Iran's response to
OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FThe fragile ceasefire was tested when
OL,8,Fa drone ignited a small fire on a ship
OL,9,Foff Qatar and the United Arab Emirates
OL,10,Fand Kuwait reported drones entering
OL,11,Ftheir airspace.
OL,13,FThe UAE said it shot down two drones
OL,14,Fand blamed Iran. No casualties were
OL,15,Freported, and no one immediately
OL,16,Fclaimed responsibility.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
