OL,3,CTrump says Iran's response to
OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FQatar's Foreign Ministry called the
OL,8,Fship attack a "dangerous and
OL,9,Funacceptable escalation that threatens
OL,10,Fthe security and safety of maritime
OL,11,Ftrade routes and vital supplies in the
OL,12,Fregion."
OL,14,FThe United Kingdom Maritime Trade
OL,15,FOperations Centre gave no details
OL,16,Fabout the ship's owner or origin.
OL,18,FKuwait Defence Ministry spokesperson
OL,19,FBrig. Gen. Saud Abdulaziz Al Otaibi
OL,20,Fsaid forces responded to drones but
OL,21,Fdid not say where they came from.
