OL,3,CTrump says Iran's response to
OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FIran and armed allied groups like
OL,8,FHezbollah in Lebanon have used drones
OL,9,Fto carry out hundreds of strikes since
OL,10,Fthe war began with U.S. and Israeli
OL,11,Fattacks on February 28.
OL,13,FIran says it's on 'full readiness' to
OL,14,Fprotect nuclear sites
OL,16,FTrump has reiterated threats to resume
OL,17,Ffull-scale bombing if Iran does not
OL,18,Faccept an agreement to reopen the
OL,19,Fstrait and roll back its nuclear
OL,20,Fprogram.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
