OL,3,CTrump says Iran's response to
OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FIran has largely blocked the strategic
OL,8,Fwaterway that's key to the global flow
OL,9,Fof oil, natural gas and fertilizer
OL,10,Fsince the war began, rattling world
OL,11,Fmarkets.
OL,13,FThe US military in turn has blockaded
OL,14,FIranian ports since April 13, saying
OL,15,Fit has turned back 61 commercial
OL,16,Fvessels and disabled four.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
