OL,3,CTrump says Iran's response to
OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FOn Friday, it struck two Iranian oil
OL,8,Ftankers it said were trying to breach
OL,9,Fthe blockade. Iran's Revolutionary
OL,10,FGuard navy says any attack on Iranian
OL,11,Foil tankers or commercial vessels
OL,12,Fwould be met with a "heavy assault" on
OL,13,FUS bases in the region and enemy ships.
OL,15,FAnother sticking point in negotiations
OL,16,Fis Iran's highly enriched uranium. The
OL,17,FUN's nuclear agency says Iran has more
OL,18,Fthan 440 kilograms enriched up to 60%
OL,19,Fpurity, a short, technical step from
OL,20,Fweapons grade.
OL,26,@tD@UOUtD@cO]
