OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FIn an interview posted late Saturday,
OL,8,Fan Iranian military spokesperson said
OL,9,Fforces were on "full readiness" to
OL,10,Fprotect sites where uranium is stored.
OL,12,F"We considered it possible that they
OL,13,Fmight intend to steal it through
OL,14,Finfiltration operations or heli-borne
OL,15,Foperations," Brigadier General Akrami
OL,16,FNia told the IRNA news agency.
