OL,7,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,8,FNetanyahu in an excerpt of an
OL,9,Finterview with CBS airing Sunday said
OL,10,Fthe war isn't over because the
OL,11,Fenriched uranium needs to be taken out
OL,12,Fof Iran.
OL,14,F"Trump has said to me, 'I want to go
OL,15,Fin there,' and I think it can be done
OL,16,Fphysically," he said.
