OL,3,CTrump says Iran's response to
OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FRussian President Vladimir Putin said
OL,8,FSaturday that Moscow's proposal to
OL,9,Ftake enriched uranium from Iran to
OL,10,Fhelp negotiate a settlement remains on
OL,11,Fthe table.
OL,13,FThe majority of Iran's highly enriched
OL,14,Furanium is likely at its Isfahan
OL,15,Fnuclear complex, the International
OL,16,FAtomic Energy Agency director-general
OL,17,Fsaid last month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
