OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,FThe facility was hit by US-Israeli
OL,8,Fairstrikes in the 12-day war last year
OL,9,Fand faced less intense attacks this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FIran warns against French-British
OL,13,Fefforts in Strait of Hormuz
OL,15,FIran's deputy foreign minister warned
OL,16,Fagainst a planned French-British
OL,17,Feffort that aims to support maritime
OL,18,Fsecurity in the Strait of Hormuz after
OL,19,Fhostilities are over.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
