OL,3,CTrump says Iran's response to
OL,4,Cceasefire proposal is 'totally
OL,5,Cunacceptable'
OL,7,F"The presence of French and British
OL,8,Fvessels, or those of any other
OL,9,Fcountry, for any possible cooperation
OL,10,Fwith illegal U.S. actions in the
OL,11,FStrait of Hormuz that violate
OL,12,Finternational law will be met with a
OL,13,Fdecisive and immediate response from
OL,14,Fthe armed forces," Kazem Gharibabadi
OL,15,Fsaid on social media.
OL,17,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron
OL,18,Fresponded by saying it won't be a
OL,19,Fmilitary deployment but an
OL,20,Finternational mission to secure
OL,21,Fshipping once conditions allow.
