OL,7,FSeveral attacks against ships in the
OL,8,FPersian Gulf have occurred over the
OL,9,Fpast week, and a U.S. effort to
OL,10,F"guide" ships through the strait was
OL,11,Fquickly paused.
OL,13,FSouth Korea announced initial findings
OL,14,Ffrom an investigation that said two
OL,15,Funidentified objects struck the South
OL,16,FKorean-operated vessel HMM NAMU about
OL,17,Fone minute apart while it was anchored
OL,18,Fin the strait last week, causing an
OL,19,Fexplosion and fire.
